<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Skill_Job</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
      
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background-image: url("background-image.jpg");
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .hero-content {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #e9ecef;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #e7e7e7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #008CBA;
            border-color: #008CBA;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
            .cta-button:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
                border-color: #0056b3;
            }

        .feature-box {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .feature-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }

        .job-box {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            height: 450px;
        }

            .job-box:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
            }

            .job-box img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 200px;
                object-fit: cover;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .job-box h3 {
                font-size: 20px;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                color: black; 
            }

            .job-box p {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #6c757d;
            }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   <div class="container-fluid hero-section" style="background-image: url('/Image/back.png');">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 class="hero-title">Find Your Dream Job</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Discover a world of opportunities</p>
                <a href="/Findjobs/Index" class="btn btn-primary cta-button">Browse Jobs</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="container feature-box">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <i class="bi bi-award-fill feature-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="feature-title">Skills &amp; Expertise</h2>
                <p class="feature-description">Find jobs that match your skills and expertise to advance your career.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <i class="bi bi-briefcase-fill feature-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="feature-title">Job Listings</h2>
                <p class="feature-description">Explore a wide range of job listings from various industries and companies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <i class="bi bi-building feature-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="feature-title">Companies</h2>
                <p class="feature-description">Discover reputable companies offering exciting job opportunities.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <a href="/Findjobs/Index">
                <div class="job-box">
                    <img src="https://penji.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/4.-Evolution-freeware-co-logo.jpg" alt="Job Image">
                    <h3>Software Engineer</h3>
                    <p>Total pay for a Trainee Engineer is BDT 47,500 per month.</p>
                </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <a href="/Findjobs/Index">
                <div class="job-box">
                    <img src="https://penji.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1.-Grappler-Tech-and-Devs-logo.jpg" alt="Job Image">
                    <h3>Brand Manager</h3>
                    <p>Total pay for an Officer at Beximco Pharmaceuticals is BDT 33,500 per month.</p>
                </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <a href="/Findjobs/Index">
                <div class="job-box">
                    <img src="https://penji.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/5.-Mothership-tech-house-logo.jpg" alt="Job Image">
                    <h3>Pattern Master</h3>
                    <p>Square Group Job Circular 2023 has been published on 26 &amp; 28 April 2023.</p>
                </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <a href="/Findjobs/Index">
                <div class="job-box">
                    <img src="https://penji.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/6.-Code-red-logo.jpg" alt="Job Image">
                    <h3>Marketing Executive</h3>
                    <p>Join our team as a Marketing Executive and drive growth in our organization.</p>
                </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <a href="/Findjobs/Index">
                <div class="job-box">
                    <img src="https://penji.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/8.-The-cabinet-managementy-sys-logo.jpg" alt="Job Image">
                    <h3>Graphic Designer</h3>
                    <p>We are looking for a talented Graphic Designer to create engaging visual content.</p>
                </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <a href="/Findjobs/Index">
                <div class="job-box">
                    <img src="https://penji.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/9.-Mercurial-operating-system-logo.jpg" alt="Job Image">
                    <h3>Data Analyst</h3>
                    <p>Join our Data Analytics team and help drive data-driven decision-making.</p>
                </div>
                </a>
            </div>
           
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
